items.description: A short-sleeved, color-blocked T-shirt with a bold brand logo printed on the front.
A striped shirt with three-quarter sleeves and contrast yellow trim on the cuffs and neckline.
A cropped, knit cardigan with a cable pattern and a single button closure.
A long-sleeve button-up shirt with a collar, made from a lightweight fabric.
A navy blue t-shirt with short sleeves, featuring a geometric and text design on the front in white, purple, pink, and blue.
A color-block shirt with three sections: a dark blue top section with a pocket, a navy blue middle section, and a light gray bottom section. The shirt has short sleeves.
A sleeveless quilted vest with a zipper down the front. It features a combination of materials with a knitted collar and quilted body. The vest has a small chest pocket on one side.
Distressed skinny jeans with ripped knees and a faded wash.
A long-sleeve plaid shirt with a classic collar and button-down front, featuring a multicolored checkered pattern with shades of pink, blue, yellow, and white. It also has two chest pockets.
Sleeveless shirt with a multicolored zigzag pattern.
A short-sleeved shirt with a collar and a button-up front, featuring an all-over print pattern.

A casual short-sleeve shirt with a green base color featuring white horizontal stripes and a small, scattered print design.
A pair of grey denim jeans with a button and zip closure, five-pocket design, and subtle fading.
Navy blue pajama pants featuring a pattern of white and black soccer balls and the word 'FOOTBALL'.
A black and white striped short-sleeve dress with a crew neckline. The pattern consists of horizontal stripes covering the entire dress.
A long-sleeved button-up shirt with a classic collar and plaid pattern.
A navy blue dress with a buttoned, high neckline and long sleeves. The dress has a tiered, flowing design.
A pair of casual beige shorts with an elastic waistband, designed for comfort.

A button-up shirt with a collar and short sleeves, featuring a subtle patterned design.
A casual short-sleeve t-shirt with a graphic logo and text on the front.
Short-sleeved, button-up collared shirt with a chest pocket.

A basic black t-shirt with short sleeves and a round neckline.
A cropped sweater shrug with cable knit detailing on the front and ribbed cuffs.
A puffy, short-sleeved shirt with a V-neck, featuring horizontal padded sections.
A striped, long-sleeve shirt with a yellow contrast trim on the neckline and sleeves.
A pair of white sandals with a flat sole, adjustable ankle straps, and decorative metal buckles.

A long, ribbed knit cardigan with long sleeves and an open front.
